This paper is primarily focused on facial expression recognition, which falls under the computer vision (cs.CV) category. The paper also extensively uses deep learning techniques, which are commonly used in machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI) research. Additionally, the paper discusses the creation of a new dataset, which could be relevant to the human-computer interaction (cs.HC) and multimedia (cs.MM) categories.
